36:55.130 --> 36:56.746
<i>DOCTOR:
This patient, Mr Jagjit Sanghera</i>

36:56.798 --> 36:58.835
<i>suffers from acute paranoid
schizophrenia.</i>

36:58.883 --> 37:00.749
<i>LAURA:
Let's pretend my dad was never ill.</i>

37:00.802 --> 37:01.918
<i>SATHNAM:
You know about this?</i>

37:01.970 --> 37:03.757
<i>DOCTOR:
These are for his mental health problems.</i>

37:03.805 --> 37:05.717
<i>LAURA: Let's keep the peasants
up in Wolverhampton</i>

37:05.765 --> 37:07.381
<i>while I have another life down here!</i>

37:07.434 --> 37:08.891
<i>DOCTOR:
He may think it's talking to him.</i>

37:08.935 --> 37:10.722
<i>Well, since we have seen no
aggression for many years.</i>

37:10.770 --> 37:12.056
<i>SATHNAM:
What do you mean, aggression?</i>

37:12.105 --> 37:14.313
<i>LAURA: Given you don't know the
basic facts about your own family...</i>

37:14.357 --> 37:17.816
<i>JAGJIT: But everything is OK
because I can raise the sun.</i>

37:17.861 --> 37:20.148
<i>And I have worked it out myself.</i>

37:34.919 --> 37:37.832
<i>LAURA:
Have you really never noticed anything?</i>

37:48.516 --> 37:51.259
TRAIN ROLLS BY

37:57.025 --> 37:59.392
TV PLAYS

38:01.780 --> 38:03.487
Sathnam.

38:03.531 --> 38:05.363
<i>Sathnam.
- Theek hai.</i>

38:05.408 --> 38:06.899
Sathnam, again.

38:16.711 --> 38:17.872
Dedi.

38:19.672 --> 38:20.662
SATHNAM SIGHS

38:20.715 --> 38:24.334
Can I ask about when you first
came to this country?

38:26.304 --> 38:28.887
When you... when you first came here,
when you were young.

38:30.600 --> 38:32.933
You were younger than me,
weren't you?

38:35.271 --> 38:37.433
I used to ride a bike.

38:37.482 --> 38:38.973
Did you?

38:41.110 --> 38:44.319
I used to go everywhere on it.

38:45.156 --> 38:50.026
I went to... I went everywhere
on the bike.

38:53.164 --> 38:54.655
'Everywhere.'
- Mum.

38:54.707 --> 38:58.326
He can't ride a bike.
- I can, I can.

39:04.425 --> 39:05.757
You didn't have a bike!

39:10.515 --> 39:11.801
When was that?

39:12.350 --> 39:15.309
When I first came to this
country in...

39:16.855 --> 39:18.346
1986.

39:18.398 --> 39:19.889
<i>Leh, 1986.</i>

39:19.899 --> 39:23.643
It was 1979.
- I rode a bike.

39:25.196 --> 39:27.688
I was the strongest man
in this country.

39:28.908 --> 39:31.742
And I used to... lift weights.

39:34.330 --> 39:35.821
SHE SIGHS

39:37.041 --> 39:39.203
Why you asking him all
these questions, hey?

39:39.252 --> 39:42.245
Week in, week out, I ask strangers
about their lives

39:42.297 --> 39:45.506
and I don't know the first thing
about my own family.

39:46.384 --> 39:48.546
And it turns out it's your story,
Mum.

39:48.595 --> 39:51.804
Yours and Dedi's, yeah.
How you've coped.

39:51.848 --> 39:53.510
That's the story I need to hear.

39:55.852 --> 39:57.434
I used to ride a bike.

40:11.200 --> 40:13.408
I mean, I... I don't even know
how old you were

40:13.453 --> 40:15.365
when you first met Dedi.

40:15.413 --> 40:17.450
You know, when your marriage
was arranged.

40:24.631 --> 40:25.838
Hm.

40:26.633 --> 40:27.794
15.

40:28.885 --> 40:31.468
Maybe 16.

40:35.934 --> 40:37.516
And did you know he was ill?

40:42.106 --> 40:43.096
SHE WHIMPERS LIGHTLY

40:44.901 --> 40:46.358
What did you know?

40:47.987 --> 40:51.981
Look, I don't want you to start
worrying about all this.

40:52.033 --> 40:54.901
Mum, I worry about what
I don't know.

40:55.662 --> 40:57.028
OK?

41:24.315 --> 41:26.056
SATHNAM:
And then... and then, they what?

41:26.109 --> 41:27.145
Showed you a photo?

41:27.193 --> 41:29.025
SHE CHUCKLES
Photo.

41:43.251 --> 41:45.743
SATHNAM: So you didn't
even know what he looked like?

41:59.308 --> 42:01.766
I told you about Sikh girl.

42:01.811 --> 42:04.849
I have a number for her now.
She's a doctor.

42:04.897 --> 42:06.433
<i>Mum, Mum...
- Doctore.</i>

42:06.482 --> 42:09.850
Mum, this is about you, not me.

42:10.820 --> 42:11.981
OK?

42:12.905 --> 42:14.237
Go on.

42:23.624 --> 42:24.990
SHE SIGHS

42:37.138 --> 42:39.175
MAN SINGS IN PUNJABI

42:53.905 --> 42:56.397
MAN RECITES IN PUNJABI

43:00.578 --> 43:02.615
SATHNAM'S MOTHER SPEAKS
IN PUNJABI

43:04.582 --> 43:05.993
RECITATION CONTINUES

43:17.303 --> 43:20.467
He just sat there.

43:24.894 --> 43:26.556
And what happened after that?

43:28.648 --> 43:32.437
